<p>The Pupil is a child of the colony. The <a href="../workers/teacher">Teacher</a> will teach the Pupils at the School to increase the Pupilsâ€™ skill levels. While the Teacher can teach with no supplies, providing paper will increase the speed that the Pupils level.</p>

<p>While they are not technically the worker of the School (the Teacher is), the School is where hire the Pupils to learn.</p>
